               <p>NATHANIEL CROSSLAND. I live in <placeName id="t18291203-207-crimeloc1068">Brick-lane, St. Luke's</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18291203-207-crimeloc1068" type="placeName" value="Brick-lane, St. Luke's"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18291203-207-crimeloc1068" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291203-207-off1066 t18291203-207-crimeloc1068"></join>. I lost a piece of pork from my window last Saturday, at half-past seven o'clock in the morning; the tray in which it stood was full two feet from the window - a girl who was lighting the fire said some person had taken a dish of pork; I ran out and saw the prisoner carrying it up Seward-street; I followed him - he saw me, threw it down; and ran off; I called Stop thief! several persons came up, and met him - he turned back, and I took him; my little boy was close after me, and he took the pork up- when I brought the prisoner back, he offered to pay for the dish.</p>
               <p>EDWARD BURFORT. I saw the prisoner come into Seward-street, with the pork, and a ticket on it; I saw him throw it down, and the prosecutor took him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18291203-207-person1282">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CHURCHILL
               <interp inst="t18291203-207-person1282" type="surname" value="CHURCHILL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291203-207-person1282" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291203-207-person1282" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going down Brick-lane, and saw a young man go past; he took this dish off the window, and gave it to me - I went up Seward-street; the prosecutor came after me - I put down the dish, and he took me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18291203-207-verdict1069" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291203-207-verdict1069" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
